Cate's favourite brand SK-II, for which she has been an ambassador for 11 years, have today released their new product, SK-II Mid-Day Miracle Essence.

The new product is SK-II's cult Facial Treatment Essence product in spray form, which can be used to refresh and revive the skin throughout the day. 

The formula uses Pitera, a yeast strain from Japan rich in vitamins, amino acids, minerals and organic acids, and penetrates beneath the make-up to hydrate the skin whilst the unique moisture-lock complex ensures it stays that way.

