'This year, SK-II made sure I was well prepared with the launch of my new favourite handbag product, SK-II Mid-Day Miracle Essence with Pitera. 

'Just a few spritz and it instantly revives my skin and keeps my make-up looking fresh with long-lasting moisture throughout the ceremony.'

